* 利伍德泵站（{{Lang-en|Leawood Pumphouse}} ）今为一营业之博物馆，至今仍事其本职工作，即自德文特河泵水至克罗姆福德运河。泵房于指定的周末开放。
* 在贝柏则有大量遗产点转而作其他商业之用，[[贝柏北厂|贝柏北厂]]（{{Lang-en|Belper North Mill}} ）的建筑为德文特河谷游客中心所居。其以关于德文特河谷纺织工业之历史的机械及其他物什之陈列为特色。<ref>{{Citation|url=http://www.belpernorthmill.org.uk/|title=Welcome to Belper North Mill|publisher=BelperNorthMill.org.uk|access-date=2009-06-10|archive-date=2009-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090314083405/http://belpernorthmill.org.uk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 于遗产地之极南处，约翰·洛姆的丝织厂今作[[德比工业博物馆|德比工业博物馆]]用。<ref>{{Citation|url=http://www.derby.gov.uk/LeisureCulture/MuseumsGalleries/Derby_Industrial_Museum.htm|title=The Silk Mill: Derby's Museum of Industry and History.|publisher=Derby City Council|access-date=2009-06-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221113752/http://www.derby.gov.uk/LeisureCulture/MuseumsGalleries/Derby_Industrial_Museum.htm|archivedate=2009-02-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 此博物馆于2011年4月3日关闭，封存超过两年。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thisisderbyshire.co.uk/news/Don-t-allow-valuable-museum-sacrificed/article-3268056-detail/article.html|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120527085009/http://www.thisisderbyshire.co.uk/news/Don-t-allow-valuable-museum-sacrificed/article-3268056-detail/article.html|archivedate=2012-05-27|title=Don't allow this valuable museum to be sacrificed|date=2015-02-25|work=Derby Telegraph|accessdate=2020-11-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 2013年10月一项目以为21世纪重新发明丝织厂而作者始行，合并STEAM（科学、技术、工程、艺术及数学五词于英文中之首字母集合）诸原理。此博物馆今每周开放4天。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Derby Museums|url=http://www.derbymuseums.org/thesilkmill/|accessdate=2014-01-05|publisher=Derby City Council /Derby Museums|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210221707/http://www.derbymuseums.org/thesilkmill/|archivedate=2013-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

